# 🏗️ ARCHITECT PROMPT - LAPLACE

## Role

Architect AI - Thiết kế hệ thống cho nền tảng quản lý cho thuê trọ LaPlace.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Server | Node.js 22 + Express.js 5 |
| ORM | Sequelize 6 + MySQL 8.0 |
| Admin | React 18 + Refine 4 + Ant Design 5 + Vite |
| Client | Next.js 15 + React 19 + Tailwind CSS |
| Real-time | Socket.io 4 |

---

## Project Structure

```
laplace/
├── server/              # Backend API (Express + Sequelize)
│   └── src/
│       ├── controlers/  # API Controllers (10 files)
│       ├── models/      # Sequelize Models (19 models)
│       ├── routes/      # Express Routes (8 modules)
│       ├── services/    # Business Logic (13 services)
│       ├── middlewares/  # Auth, Role, Upload (4 files)
│       ├── migrations/  # Database Migrations (19 files)
│       ├── seeders/     # Seed Data (4 files)
│       ├── core/        # Core utilities
│       ├── helpers/     # Helper functions
│       ├── utils/       # Utility functions
│       ├── socket/      # Socket.io handlers
│       └── server.js    # Entry point
├── admin/               # Admin Panel (Refine + Vite)
│   └── src/
│       ├── pages/       # Resource Pages (34 dirs, 13 legacy)
│       ├── components/  # React Components (49 files)
│       ├── providers/   # Auth & Data Providers
│       ├── styles/      # CSS Styles
│       └── App.tsx      # Main App
├── client/              # Customer Website (Next.js 15)
│   └── src/
│       ├── app/         # App Router
│       │   ├── (public)/    # 14 public page groups
│       │   ├── (auth)/      # 5 auth pages
│       │   ├── tai-khoan/   # 8 account pages
│       │   └── chu-tro/     # 7 landlord pages
│       ├── components/  # React Components
│       ├── lib/         # Utilities & API client
│       └── store/       # Zustand State
└── docker-compose.yml
```

