## API Response Format

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [...],
  "meta": {
    "total": 100,
    "page": 1,
    "limit": 20,
    "totalPages": 5
  }
}
```

---

## Server vs Client Components (Next.js 15)

| Server Component (Default) | Client Component ('use client') |
|---------------------------|--------------------------------|
| Data fetching | useState, useEffect |
| Static content | Event handlers (onClick) |
| SEO-critical pages | Browser APIs |
| Layout components | Forms, interactivity |

---

## Ports Configuration (Docker)

| Service | Port | Container |
|---------|------|-----------|
| Server API | 7201 (→8000) | laplace_server |
| Admin Panel | 7202 | laplace_admin |
| Client Website | 7203 | laplace_client |
| phpMyAdmin | 7204 | laplace_phpmyadmin |
| MySQL | 7205 (→3306) | laplace_mysql |

---

*Ref: `docker-compose.yml`, `server/src/models/`*
